That appears to be an issue with select2 ([see this demo](http://jsfiddle.net/eGXPe/382/)):

If the data includes an empty string, then you'll get blank entries. So I would add a check to see if the (trimmed) string is not empty before adding it as an option:

```js
$.each(arry, function(i,v){
  if ( $.trim(v) !== '' ) {
    data.push({id: v, text: v});
  }
});
```

